'''Dayan Kodua''' (wodzi le 7 '''[[Anyɔnyɔ]]''' 1980) nye [[Dzamanya]] fefewɔla, agbalẽŋlɔla kple kpɔɖeŋu si tso [[Gana|Ghana]] dzidzimeviwo me.<ref>http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/entertainment/Ghanaian-Born-For-Miss-Germany-2002-21234?gallery=1</ref><ref>https://www.deutschland.de/en/topic/life/society-integration/my-germany-actor-dayan-kodua</ref><ref>https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/Former-UN-expert-3-others-receive-Nana-Yaa-Asantewaa-Award-505642</ref> Le ƒe 2001 me la, eva zu nyɔnu ameyibɔ gbãtɔ kple ɖeka kolia si ɖu dzi le atsyɔ̃ɖoɖo ƒe hoʋiʋli aɖe me le Germany. Ewɔ akpa vevi aɖe le Amerika kple Germany sinima geɖewo me eye wode bubu eŋu be enye amedɔdɔ na Afrika-nyigbagã le Germany le ƒe 2005 me.<ref>https://www.bild.de/regional/hamburg/hamburg-aktuell/dayan-kodua-neue-rolle-gegen-alte-klischees-59072290.bild.html</ref><ref>http://lafritude.com/?p=4472</ref>

